Potential Enhancements
1. Visual & UX Improvements
Dark Mode Toggle - Add a light/dark theme switcher
Loading Skeletons - Show skeleton screens while data loads instead of plain "Loading..."
Empty States - Add illustrations or better messaging for empty states
Toast Notifications - Replace alerts with modern toast notifications
Image Zoom - Click to zoom chemical structure images
Sorting Options - Sort chemicals by name, formula, or recently added
2. Functionality Enhancements
Advanced Search - Search by formula, CAS number, or properties (not just name)
Bulk Operations - Select multiple chemicals to export or delete
Chemical Comparison - Compare properties of 2-3 chemicals side-by-side
Print View - Optimized print layout for chemical details
QR Code Generation - Generate QR codes for chemical details (useful for lab labels)
Chemical Calculator - Molecular weight calculator, dilution calculator
3. Data & Organization
Categories/Collections - Group chemicals into custom collections
Recent Activity - Show recently viewed chemicals
Notes System - Add personal notes to chemicals
Related Chemicals - Show similar or related chemicals
Data Validation - Better form validation with helpful error messages
4. Progressive Web App (PWA)
Offline Mode - Work without internet connection
Install Prompt - Add "Install App" button
Push Notifications - Reminders for chemical inventory checks
5. Accessibility & Performance
Keyboard Shortcuts - Quick navigation (e.g., / to focus search)
Screen Reader Improvements - Better ARIA labels
Performance Optimization - Lazy loading, code splitting
Export Options - Export to PDF, CSV, or Excel
6. Lab-Specific Features
Inventory Tracking - Track quantities and locations
Expiration Dates - Alert for chemicals nearing expiration
Safety Checklists - Pre-use safety checklists
Barcode Scanner - Scan chemical barcodes (using device camera)
